<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-584-431  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 584 431.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Data Based Advisor  Nov 1990 v8 n11 p68(2)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Data Based Solutions 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Accounting software release offers dBASE record-retrieval utility.andO;(Comsoft Inc's ABACUS II) (The Complete Comdex Catalog 1990)(product announcement)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   Comsoft Inc. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   Abacus II (Accounting software) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     AccountingProduct IntroductionSoftware Packages.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Accounting Software Release Offers dBASE Record-Retrieval UtilityandM;EDMONTON, ALBERTA--Comsoft Inc. announced its new ABACUS II accountingsoftware.andP;  According to the company, they designed this version from theground up for network use.andP;  Once a document is entered into the data screens,the effect of entries ripple throughout the program, distributing theinformation wherever it's needed.andP;  The data screens look like familiar paperforms.andP;  The program retains details of each transaction of a company'sbusiness for the entire fiscal year--for immediate recall.andM;The program also contains db DETECTIVE, a dBASE record-retrieval utility,which can run either memory-resident or stand-alone.andP;  The utility searchesnon-indexed fields in dBASE-compatible files at speeds that range from 300 to1,000 records per second.andP;  Other features include: a Norton Commander-likefile manager; business graphics; a Lotus 1-2-3-like spreadsheet; aWordStar-like text editor; disaster control; a data dictionary;user-definable fields; and a pop-up calculator.andM;ABACUS II Basic, including GL, AP, and AR, is priced at $1,695.andP;  The JobEstimating/Costing and Inventory modules cost $849.andP;  For more information,contact Comsoft Inc., (403) 489-5994.andO;</TEXT></DOC>